[70]NPR Extra

[71]NPR and Member stations win 2025 Gracie Awards

   by [72] Sommer Hill

   [73]March 25, 2025 

[74]NPR Extra

[75]Jay Shaylor will be the new 'Morning Edition' and 'Up First' Executive
Producer

   [76]February 3, 2025  After a nationwide search we are pleased to
   announce Jay Shaylor will be the next Executive Producer of Morning
   Edition and Up First.

   NPR Extra — from NPR's Communications Team — is the place to come for
   organizational news and announcements.

   We also share the occasional peek behind the scenes at the people and
   personalities who deliver the news to you every day.

   [77]Visit the About section for more about NPR's mission, values, and
   connections. You can also connect with us directly via [78]our contact
   form.

